{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_016", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "叶辰在路上遇到一个卖花的盲眼老婆婆，老婆婆说他的命格很特别。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "老婆婆其实是天机阁的阁主伪装的，她算到叶辰是改变天地大劫的关键人物。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_017", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "系统商店里有一个标价999999积分的商品，从来没人买得起。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "那是一枚'天道令'，持有者可以调动一次天道之力。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_018", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "叶辰在秘境中得到了一面铜镜，镜面模糊照不出人影。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "铜镜需要在月圆之夜用精血激活，激活后可以照出千里之外的景象。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_019", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "王猛家族祠堂中供着一把断剑，没有人知道它的来历。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "断剑的另一半在叶辰手中——这两半合在一起就是上古神器'斩天剑'。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_020", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "叶辰每次闭关都能听到一个声音在念诵经文，出关后就消失了。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "那是他前世的师尊在通过神识传音，指导他修炼的关键。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_021", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "宗门的考核石碑上有一个无人能通过的第二关——心魔关。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "心魔关的试炼内容是直面自己最恐惧的记忆。叶辰在心魔关中看到了前世被背叛的场景。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_022", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "叶辰救下了一只被追杀的幼年妖兽，妖兽一直跟着他不肯走。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "幼年妖兽是上古神兽白虎的后裔，成长起来后拥有毁天灭地的力量。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_023", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "拍卖会上出现了一颗无人识别的丹药，药香弥漫了整个会场。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "那是上古丹帝炼制的'轮回丹'，服用后可保留记忆转世重生。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_024", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "叶辰在天机阁花了一万灵石买了一句话：'小心身边的人'。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "他身边的人——他的师弟——其实是仇家派来的卧底。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_025", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "系统提示有一个隐藏任务从未被触发过：'远古的呼唤'。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "任务的触发条件是持有五件特定的上古遗物，完成任务后可以获得创世神的传承。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_026", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "叶辰在拍卖会上买了一块废铁，所有人都笑他人傻钱多。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "废铁是一块天外陨铁，是打造神器的核心材料。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_027", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "王猛在梦中经常看到一座金色的宫殿，醒来后头痛欲裂。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "金色宫殿是上古神族的神殿遗址，王猛的神族血脉在召唤他前往。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_028", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "宗门的后山上有一块刻满符文的石碑，没人能解读。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "石碑上记载的是上古大战的历史和魔王的封印地点。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_029", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "叶辰在茶楼听书时，说书人讲了一个关于'天选之人'的故事。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "说书人讲的不是故事，而是真实发生过的事——天选之人就是叶辰的前世。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_030", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "叶辰的储物戒指中有一块不知从哪来的玉简，打不开。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "玉简是前世大战时封印的记忆，需要达到大乘期才能解开。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_031", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "宗门附近的村民说山里有'山神'显灵，丢的东西会自己回来。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "所谓山神是一只擅长偷窃的灵猴，它偷东西后会模仿山神显灵来捉弄村民。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 4, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 16}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_032", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "叶辰发现自己的系统界面偶尔会出现一些乱码。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "乱码是系统在试图提示他——这个世界存在一个被上层力量抹除的'隐藏种族'。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_033", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "王猛在河里洗澡时捡到一块会发热的石头。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "石头是火麒麟的内丹碎片，附近有火麒麟的巢穴。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.9, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_034", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "叶辰收到了一封没有署名的战书，约他在三年后决战。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "下战书的是他前世最大的敌人——冥帝。三年的时间是给他的'准备期'。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_xuanhuan_035", "genre": "xuanhuan", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "宗门的老祖画像中，有一个人的面容模糊不清，像是被刻意抹去了。", "context": "", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 0, "text": "那个人是叛出宗门的前任大弟子，他后来成了魔道的创始人之一。", "context": "", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
